title: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup issue
description: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup method is not behaving as expected.
OB: When calling onStartup method with a Set<Class<?>> classSet, the output is "MySomeClass".
SR: Steps to reproduce: 1. Call the onStartup method with a Set<Class<?>> classSet. 2. Check the output and see if it is not equal to "MySomeClass".
